K-DASH Purses and Handbags are rooted in the designs of higher end bags. Accessorize with these K-DASH purses and handbags that are truly stylin. K-DASH is a Kardashian Clothing and Womens accessories line that brought to the world by QVC network. Clicking through on any of the KDASH items will take you to the QVC.com website and K-DASH item directly. The Kardashians Kim, Kourtney, and Kloe all advertise K-DASH via the QVC television regularly. They explain the details of each item and personally approve the designs and workmanship. These K-DASH purses and handbags are of high quality and from the Kardashian Clothing sense of style.
